{"tid":1594044,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"若紅魔棄將盧卡古本輪再入球 將追平巴西朗拿度紀錄","createTime":"2019-09-25T10:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T01:07:03.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3d326918f842e29f2e9d62010c58351a3ba875c9","tid":1594044,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:59:19.000Z","msg":"據《都靈體育報》統計，如果盧卡古（R.Lukaku）能在本輪國米對陣拉素的比賽中取得入球，那麼他就將追平兩位國米名宿朗拿度（Ronaldo）和米列圖（D.Milito）的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n  加盟國米以來，盧卡古已經在4場意甲聯賽中斬獲3球，而此前只有朗拿度和米列圖兩位名宿曾在加盟國米後的前5場比賽中攻入至少4球。<br />\n<br />\n  《都靈體育報》稱，如果盧卡古能在對陣拉素的比賽中取得入球，那麼他也將在加盟國米後的前5場比賽攻入至少4球，從而追平兩位國米名宿朗拿度和米列圖的紀錄"},{"pid":"bd770b9127c8a59b9c8e4367545dc3e9d0c1f51e","tid":1594044,"uid":92603,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"玩到咁細緻既紀錄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f23be6c93ce6df1e81999b9d47bb7fd5809ceb9","tid":1594044,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd770b9127c8a59b9c8e4367545dc3e9d0c1f51e","tid":1594044,"uid":92603,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"玩到咁細緻既紀錄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:09:03.000Z","msg":"可能玩玩下變國米單季聯賽最多入波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f297abcc33b84dd669b46d5dec193e444356c48","tid":1594044,"uid":48939,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"bd770b9127c8a59b9c8e4367545dc3e9d0c1f51e","tid":1594044,"uid":92603,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"玩到咁細緻既紀錄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:26:56.000Z","msg":"大佬 而家講緊比利時神鋒 緊係要攞D傳奇人物比較 先對得住魔性爆炸嘅LKK"},{"pid":"c9d96035fb0f9d524fcad821eaf6bc8c7639438e","tid":1594044,"uid":118973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:28:35.000Z","msg":"好勁咩 <br />\n